{"tid":1317513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果A1:浴血新城市","createTime":"2019-07-14T19:05:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T00:49:11.000Z","uid":240362,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"770f1e06c30b37b27e7d385f4c1fc6e148e2cf88","tid":1317513,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:05:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/66529535_10157843579607448_2204468415089868800_n.jpg?_nc_cat=110&amp;_nc_oc=AQlsWMZ0OZEuS3U7D88QePTbWV4af8HM0iuwnFVw7H6gOc1hYx14Tg5coEO9z7K7QNk&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=fb3919d1a769a1075e55cefaebb5d86a&amp;oe=5DA3279F\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F66529535_10157843579607448_2204468415089868800_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D110%26_nc_oc%3DAQlsWMZ0OZEuS3U7D88QePTbWV4af8HM0iuwnFVw7H6gOc1hYx14Tg5coEO9z7K7QNk%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3Dfb3919d1a769a1075e55cefaebb5d86a%26oe%3D5DA3279F&h=9582dac8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8fc25d21f2e85649c9416db513894192dfe17b6f","tid":1317513,"uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:05:11.000Z","msg":"【A1頭條】沙田新城市廣場昨晚爆發示威者與警方大混戰。昨午5時起，參與遊行的示威者與警方在源禾路及沙田鄉事會路對峙，晚上8 時多警方開始推進，先於好運中心附近爆發衝突；近10時過百名示威者被防暴警察逼退至新城市廣場內，雙方激烈衝突，示威者向防暴警察投擲雨傘，防暴警察用警棍驅散及圍毆示威者，甚至在商場內施放胡椒噴劑，衝突持續逾一小時，醫管局共接獲22人受傷送院，20 男17女被帶返警署。一直在場調停的民主黨議員鄺俊宇批評警方清場行動「離晒大譜，草菅人命」，要求成立獨立調查委員會調查所有反送中衝突事件。"},{"pid":"a68fd19d212fd4ef16438da0e30bedbe90be7813","tid":1317513,"uid":28921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:06:37.000Z","msg":"個頭條好有動感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7b4434fcd3018cf9e448f1e8a9147f4902683f9","tid":1317513,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T00:46:12.000Z","msg":"今日個標題咁爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a